{"pageProps":{"bookInfo":{"id":"24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622","name":"高性能的mysql","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql","chapterList":[{"id":"24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622_24fa845e25adb12aa70795d5ab0e3058","type":"chapter","name":"01mysql 逻辑架构.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql\\01mysql 逻辑架构.md","url":"/chapter/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622_24fa845e25adb12aa70795d5ab0e3058"},{"id":"24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622_e7deb2976085904fdb60f28f10820220","type":"chapter","name":"02mysql 基准测试.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql\\02mysql 基准测试.md","url":"/chapter/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622_e7deb2976085904fdb60f28f10820220"},{"id":"24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622_54ad46cd31428b8bcb1dce519c9a1a67","type":"chapter","name":"03服务器性能剖析.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\database\\高性能的mysql\\03服务器性能剖析.md","url":"/chapter/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622_54ad46cd31428b8bcb1dce519c9a1a67"}],"title":"01mysql 逻辑架构","type":"book","url":"/book/24a708d3308af7484babaa7ac3c53622","content":"\n    \n    \n      <div class=\"crossnote markdown-preview  \">\n      \n<h1 id=\"mysql逻辑架构\">mysql逻辑架构 </h1>\n<pre data-role=\"codeBlock\" data-info=\"\" class=\"language-text\"><code>        ----------------------------------------\n        |                客户端                 |\n        ----------------------------------------\n        |              连接\\/线程处理            |\n        ----------------------------------------\n        |     查询缓存       |       解析器      |\n        ----------------------------------------\n        |                 优化器                |\n        ----------------------------------------\n        |                 存储引擎              |\n        ----------------------------------------\n\n</code></pre><h1 id=\"并发控制\">并发控制 </h1>\n<h2 id=\"读写锁\">读写锁 </h2>\n<h2 id=\"锁粒度\">锁粒度 </h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>锁策略 就是在锁的开销和数据的安全性之间寻求平衡</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"表锁\">表锁 </h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>最基本的锁策略，并且是开销最小的策略<br>\n会锁定整个表</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"行级锁\">行级锁 </h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>最大程度的支持并发处理，同时也会带来最大的锁开销</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"事务\">事务 </h1>\n<h2 id=\"a-atomicity-原子性-不可分割的最小工作单元\">A atomicity 原子性 不可分割的最小工作单元 </h2>\n<h2 id=\"c-comnsistency-一致性\">C comnsistency 一致性 </h2>\n<h2 id=\"i-isolation-隔离性\">I isolation 隔离性 </h2>\n<h2 id=\"d-durability-持久性\">D durability 持久性 </h2>\n<h2 id=\"隔离级别\">隔离级别 </h2>\n<h3 id=\"未提交读-read-uncomitted\">未提交读 read uncomitted </h3>\n<h3 id=\"提交读-read-committed\">提交读 read committed </h3>\n<h3 id=\"可重复读-repeatable-read\">可重复读 repeatable read </h3>\n<h3 id=\"可串行化-serializable\">可串行化 serializable </h3>\n<h2 id=\"死锁\">死锁 </h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2个事务或者多个在同一个资源上相互占用，请求锁定对方占用的资源，从而导致恶性循环的现象</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md-sidebar-toc\">\n<div class=\"md-toc\">\n<div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px\">\n          <a href=\"#mysql逻辑架构\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>mysql逻辑架构</p>\n\n          </a></div><details style=\"padding:0;;padding-left:0px;\" open=\"\">\n        <summary class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\">\n          <a href=\"#并发控制\" class=\"md-toc-link\"><p>并发控制</p>\n</a>\n          </summary>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#读写锁\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>读写锁</p>\n\n          </a></div><details style=\"padding:0;;padding-left:24px;\" open=\"\">\n        <summary class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\">\n          <a href=\"#锁粒度\" class=\"md-toc-link\"><p>锁粒度</p>\n</a>\n          </summary>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#表锁\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>表锁</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#行级锁\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>行级锁</p>\n\n          </a></div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n    \n        </div>\n      </details>\n    <details style=\"padding:0;;padding-left:0px;\" open=\"\">\n        <summary class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\">\n          <a href=\"#事务\" class=\"md-toc-link\"><p>事务</p>\n</a>\n          </summary>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#a-atomicity-原子性-不可分割的最小工作单元\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>A atomicity 原子性 不可分割的最小工作单元</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#c-comnsistency-一致性\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>C comnsistency 一致性</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#i-isolation-隔离性\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>I isolation 隔离性</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#d-durability-持久性\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>D durability 持久性</p>\n\n          </a></div><details style=\"padding:0;;padding-left:24px;\" open=\"\">\n        <summary class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\">\n          <a href=\"#隔离级别\" class=\"md-toc-link\"><p>隔离级别</p>\n</a>\n          </summary>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#未提交读-read-uncomitted\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>未提交读 read uncomitted</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#提交读-read-committed\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>提交读 read committed</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#可重复读-repeatable-read\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>可重复读 repeatable read</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#可串行化-serializable\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>可串行化 serializable</p>\n\n          </a></div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n    <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#死锁\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>死锁</p>\n\n          </a></div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n    \n</div>\n</div>\n      <a id=\"sidebar-toc-btn\">≡</a>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n<script>\n\nvar sidebarTOCBtn = document.getElementById('sidebar-toc-btn')\nsidebarTOCBtn.addEventListener('click', function(event) {\n  event.stopPropagation()\n  if (document.body.hasAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')) {\n    document.body.removeAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')\n  } else {\n    document.body.setAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc', true)\n  }\n})\n</script>\n      \n  \n    "},"title":"01mysql 逻辑架构"},"__N_SSG":true}